Build-Type:       Simple
Extra-Source-Files:
  Makefile
  publications/publications.tex
  publications/publications.bib
  hackage/hackage.tex
  hackage/thielemann.tex

Source-Repository head
  type:     darcs
  location: http://code.haskell.org/~thielema/bibtex/

